- bean curd in soy sauce
- fried tofu

reviews.text: We've ordered pan-fried tofu with minced mud carp fillings, sweet soy bean dessert with black glutinous rice, tasty and reasonable priced, open till 11pm good for after dinner, a nice place for Tofu fans and veggies. The Old lady who served us is friendly and giving us a warm welcome.
Good vegetarian noodles, fresh Soya Milk drink. Good portion, reasonable prices, good services. Have patronise many times.
Good soyabean snacks and drinks. Liked the almond / Sb plus coconut and Sb mix... the pan fried Sb was good too. Enjoy

Take a rest from shopping and great Chinese snack at this place after shopping! Soy bean kinds from juice to dessert, fried fish paste stuffed tofu etc. It’s a small basic shop with long history back but great food.
A very nice tofu shop offering various kind of bean curb products and dessert.

result.name: 人和荳品廠

reviews.text: 不錯嘅小食😊
好吃😋

#cassiegocwb
-
每日瘦編翻工有好多工作要做，所以忙到得下午茶時間先有時間食！正當我諗住去篤串魚蛋嘅時候，就見到依間人和荳品。其實每次經過都想食，因為深水埗個開公和真係好好食，雖然兩間好似無分別。😂
-
一入到伙計好有澳牛嘅style，好豪氣咁叫你自己搵位坐，我仲發現有旅客專登黎tim。秒速叫左杯熱無糖豆漿($7)同一碟魚肉煎豆腐($16 四件)。💕
-
魚肉煎豆腐好熱好脆，岩岩煎起，一定要配埋醬油先好食。熱無糖豆漿好足豆味，不過落糖一定好飲啲，但我又想健康啲。最後係唔夠飽，要再去篤魚蛋。🙈
-
味道評分▶️🌕🌕🌕🌕🌑 (4)
抵食評分▶️️🌕🌕🌕🌗🌑 (3.5)
回購評分▶️️🌕🌕🌕🌗🌑 (3.5)
-
➡️人和荳品廠 (銅鑼灣)
📍銅鑼灣渣甸街55號

將豆腐製造過程優化。店內地方整油潔。
無豆渣或煮豆時之難聞氣味。
以現今科技，製成細滑豆漿，再製成嫩滑豆腐花及用作煎豆腐或鹵豆腐。好味！

We've ordered pan-fried tofu with minced mud carp fillings, sweet soy bean dessert with black glutinous rice, tasty and reasonable priced, open till 11pm good for after dinner, a nice place for Tofu fans and veggies. The Old lady who served us is friendly and giving us a warm welcome.
